race.description: Girls Day Out 7th March C,G&E Handicap
race.comment: INNERVISIONS (11) is a consistent conveyance who has hit the frame in all five runs this campaign and has placed four of five over this six-furlong journey. Drawn to get a cosy run in transit from the inside marble and his only victory came on Soft going. Looks to get plenty in his favour today. THE GAMBLING GREEK (9) has turned in some very consistent figures this campaign, but strikes a very suitable race this time around. The sting out of the ground won't hurt and the small field is somewhat of an advantage to him. Can sit handy and be hard to run down. SUPER QUICK (3) grows a leg for hoop Cormack who has two wins from as many steers. Should give backers a sight.
